title: NYX Mega Shine Lip Gloss, Plush Red, 0.37 Ounce
description: NYX’s signature lip gloss offers a creamy, lacquer finish with high-impact color pay-off and incredible shine and sheen. This makeup artist favorite can be used as both a gloss or a stain depending on application technique.

title: Z Palette Large Black
description: Our makeup palette is an exclusive custom designed palette perfect for display and for easy color comparison of makeups. They feature a sleek and clean design that offers the strength of a plastic palette, while using eco-friendly recyclable materials. You can fold the top portion completely under the bottom portion to save on space. The Z Palette is the makeup palette that includes both a clear window and an open magnetic base to fit any size shadow, blush, bronzer, and even some foundations. You can replace the colors in your makeup palette as often as you would like.
